---
title: Miso Pesto Shrimp Ramen with Spinach and Enoki Mushrooms
description: Miso is a traditional Japanese condiment made by fermenting soybeans. You may recognize it from the very popular 'miso soup', but tonight, we're using miso in a whole new way. The combination of salty miso, sweet soy and bright green cilantro combine for something special!
